<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Inter', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 40px 20px; }
        .header { margin-bottom: 30px; text-align: center; }
        .content { background: #fff; padding: 40px; border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid #eee; box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); }
        .details-grid { background: #f9f9f9; padding: 25px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 25px 0; }
        .detail-row { margin-bottom: 15px; display: flex; align-items: baseline; }
        .detail-label { font-size: 13px; color: #777; width: 100px; font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase; }
        .detail-value { font-size: 16px; color: #111; font-weight: 500; }
        .footer { margin-top: 30px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #999; }
        h1 { color: #111; font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 10px; }
        .highlight { color: #000; font-weight: 600; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <strong>{{clinicName}}</strong>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <h1>Cita Confirmada</h1>
            <p>Hola <span class="highlight">{{patientName}}</span>, tu cita ha sido programada exitosamente.</p>
            
            <div class="details-grid">
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <div class="detail-label">Servicio</div>
                    <div class="detail-value">{{treatmentName}}</div>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <div class="detail-label">Especialista</div>
                    <div class="detail-value">{{doctorName}}</div>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <div class="detail-label">Fecha</div>
                    <div class="detail-value">{{date}}</div>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <div class="detail-label">Hora</div>
                    <div class="detail-value">{{time}}</div>
                </div>
                {{#if location}}
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <div class="detail-label">📍 Ubicación</div>
                    <div class="detail-value">{{location}}</div>
                </div>
                {{/if}}
            </div>

            <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #666;">Si necesitas reprogramar o cancelar tu cita, por favor contáctanos con al menos 24 horas de anticipación.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            Enviado via Deviaty Hub para {{clinicName}}.
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
